    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2025-03-27</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2025-05-23T18:04:30Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Expanding Appalachia’s Broadband Access Act</strong></p><p>This bill requires the Government Accountability Office to study and report to Congress on the Appalachian Regional Commission’s capability to incorporate low-orbit satellites in broadband projects. Specifically, the study must review and analyze the capacity and cost-effectiveness of using satellite broadband service for business purposes and economic development.&nbsp;</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
